CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 31, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Marie Jeanne will model some of her own exquisite creations at the fashion show Nov. 6 at the A. Leo Weil School, sponsored by members of the young Women's Board of Ushers of Wesley Center AME Zion Church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Marie Jeanne" Mary Jane Shipman Brown modeling dark short sleeve dress, dark gloves, and floral wrap, in interior doorway
